  <div id="text-content_1F3BAEB0-2154-0135-D27D-22000B5A851D" class="text-block-content">
    <p>If you have <a href="/t5/Instructor-Guide/How-do-I-allow-students-to-like-replies-in-a-discussion/ta-p/1027" target="_blank">allowed liking for a course discussion</a>, you can like discussion replies.</p>
<p>If the steps in this lesson do not match what is displayed in your course, learn how to <a href="/t5/Instructor-Guide/How-do-I-like-a-reply-in-a-course-discussion-in-Discussions/ta-p/469511" target="_blank">like replies in the Discussions Redesign interface</a>.</p>
  </div>
</div>

      <div class="step screensteps-section screensteps-depth-1" id="open_discussions" data-step-uuid="7377c4b7-7207-4c51-a83f-9409d75a6065">
    <h2 id="open_discussions" class="step-title screensteps-heading">Open Discussions</h2>
        <div class="image screensteps-image">
      <img src="https://media.screensteps.com/image_assets/assets/002/762/675/original/e18d3926-5b45-4349-a0ef-c22526140cdd.png" srcset="" alt="Open Discussions" height="258" width="175">
  </div>
 
      <div class="step-instructions screensteps-textblock">
  <div id="text-content_1F3CF060-2154-0135-D27F-22000B5A851D" class="text-block-content">
    <p>In Course Navigation, click the <strong>Discussions</strong> link.</p>
  </div>
</div>
 
  </div>

      <div class="step screensteps-section screensteps-depth-1" id="open_discussion" data-step-uuid="3908b4e7-1d31-4506-af73-7272c9ab9d2d">
    <h2 id="open_discussion" class="step-title screensteps-heading">Open Discussion</h2>
        <div class="image screensteps-image">
      <a href="https://media.screensteps.com/image_assets/assets/003/214/515/original/2cb14745-66eb-42e7-87e5-73b5865aac1b.png" class="screensteps-image-zoom" target="_blank" rel="nofollow noopener noreferrer">
        <img src="https://media.screensteps.com/image_assets/assets/003/214/515/medium/2cb14745-66eb-42e7-87e5-73b5865aac1b.png" srcset="" alt="Open Discussion" height="245" width="855">
      </a>
  </div>
 
      <div class="step-instructions screensteps-textblock">
  <div id="text-content_1F3DBE40-2154-0135-D281-22000B5A851D" class="text-block-content">
    <p>Click the name of the discussion.</p>
  </div>
</div>
 
  </div>

      <div class="step screensteps-section screensteps-depth-1" id="like_discussion_reply" data-step-uuid="c84c459d-0d90-4c71-92e5-11593bdec0b4">
    <h2 id="like_discussion_reply" class="step-title screensteps-heading">Like Discussion Reply</h2>
        <div class="image screensteps-image">
      <img src="https://media.screensteps.com/image_assets/assets/001/250/926/original/54dd1d56-0d8a-4eb5-8045-d0fa63d2089f.png" srcset="" alt="Like Discussion Reply" height="269" width="751">
  </div>
 
      <div class="step-instructions screensteps-textblock">
  <div id="text-content_1F3E8860-2154-0135-D283-22000B5A851D" class="text-block-content">
    <p>Locate the reply and click the <strong>Like </strong>icon.</p>
  </div>
</div>
 
        <div class="step screensteps-section screensteps-depth-2" id="view_liked_discussion" data-step-uuid="ceff7644-81aa-4337-87c8-6d79e3e8b167">
    <h3 id="view_liked_discussion" class="step-title screensteps-heading">View Liked Discussion</h3>
        <div class="image screensteps-image">
      <img src="https://media.screensteps.com/image_assets/assets/001/250/922/original/1a51ad22-e036-49d5-a43c-cb9213c34373.png" srcset="" alt="View Liked Discussion" height="313" width="754">
  </div>
 
      <div class="step-instructions screensteps-textblock">
  <div id="text-content_1F3F3D30-2154-0135-D285-22000B5A851D" class="text-block-content">
    <p>The Like icon will change color, indicating you have liked the reply [1].</p>
<p>The Like icon also displays the total number of times a reply has been liked [2].</p>
  </div>
</div>
 
  </div>
 
